      "title": "Three hours of power cuts for two more days",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Public Utilities Commission has allowed the Ceylon Electricity Board to extend the current three-hour power cut for two more days.",
        "Accordingly, a three-hour power cut will be implemented on July 18 and 19. This electricity cut is scheduled to be done both during the day and at night."
      ],
